snippet: The Italian coast guard says a cargo ship has rescued at least 55 migrants from Libyan waters after their rubber dinghy capsized. They say several bodies were spotted in the sea and up to 30 people might be missing....

headline.print_headline: Ship Saves 55 Migrants Off Libya; Several Die
headline.main: Ship Saves 55 Migrants Off Libya; Several Die

lead_paragraph: The Italian coast guard says a cargo ship has rescued at least 55 migrants from Libyan waters after their rubber dinghy capsized. They say several bodies were spotted in the sea and up to 30 people might be missing.
